{"tid":1313808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再叫林鄭下台！ 邊個做都一樣！口號：。五大訴求！","createTime":"2019-07-14T02:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T16:44:56.000Z","uid":58307,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc55993b32221bd7ba407bf7f493bc584681a42a","tid":1313808,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"每次都有人叫林鄭下台（係上水無），仲要叫得好頻密！<br />\n我就真心支持佢連任，We connected!<br />\n<br />\n口號集中返五大訴求！無普選就邊撚個做都一樣！<br />\n<br />\n1,徹底撤回修例<br />\n2.收回暴動定義<br />\n3.撤銷對所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n4.徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n5.以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"3948838b1c542eb686a42d28b716f0768df9e397","tid":1313808,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"全部同我入黎！教你下一步點做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313709</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7f2ac1d24fbe632794e81e4166c6cf339a1e995","tid":1313808,"uid":276156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[白宮連署] 請美國國會盡快通過 《香港民主及人權法案》</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act?fbclid=IwAR23D_JKTpK9vycdE1-cJKn8oP8a0e5IsyMCJHVyyK1YkkIqwkpM2pbI728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR23D_JKTpK9vycdE1-cJKn8oP8a0e5IsyMCJHVyyK1YkkIqwkpM2pbI728&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL0y%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=51e062c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act?fbclid=IwAR23D_JKTpK9vycdE1-cJKn8oP8a0e5IsyMCJHVyyK1YkkIqwkpM2pbI728</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>&quot;記得簽完check email confirm&quot;</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人權與民主法案（Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act）是美國討論中之法案，由美國國會及行政當局中國委員會主席眾議員克里斯&middot;史密斯、聯席主席參議員馬可&middot;魯比奧和參議員湯姆&middot;卡頓共同提出。目的是美方對涉及鎮壓基本自由的香港或中國大陸的政府官員，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">設立懲罰機制，包括禁止涉事官員入境美國及凍結其在美國之資產</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n內容:<br />\n- 重申美國對香港關係法之重視<br />\n- 美國國務卿必須每年向國會提交香港民主發展報告<br />\n- 美國國務卿必須重申對外政策上區別對待香港特別行政區政府與中華人民共和國政府<br />\n- 美國總統必須調查任何破壞香港民主人權人士之責任<br />\n- 於2014年曾參與雨傘運動的人不會因雨傘運動中被捕而被拒絕入境美國<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2019年6月重推的《香港人權和民主法案》，當中設下2020年普選立法會的「時限」，並明確要求普選特首</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"5358e083aae59b3cbee955c4d1a9452247179ad7","tid":1313808,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"林鄭依家一定唔可以下台，一下台就好多人收貨，民意會散<br />\n<br />\n另外可唔可以唔好叫「香港警察，知法犯法」？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地唔知法㗎</span></span><br />\n試著說「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港警察，企圖謀殺</span>」或其他提議"},{"pid":"1a12878f8ae96d4ad5d6b961ac3e1c51684ddad7","tid":1313808,"uid":250622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:44:56.000Z","msg":"想佢做多界"}]}